**About Bolt**

Bolt is a full-service **Design + Build** firm and fully insured **General Contractor** based in Brooklyn. We specialize in design-forward hospitality, retail, and residential projects that merge classical sensibility with innovative construction and fabrication methods. We believe that great design is only as strong as its execution — and that means being just as rigorous about budgets, schedules, and communication as we are about creative vision.

**The Role**

Bolt is seeking a **Creative Director** to lead the design vision across hospitality, retail, and residential projects and to inspire, mentor, and guide a growing team of designers. This is a senior, studio-forward role for someone who is both creatively ambitious and deeply grounded in execution.

You’ll oversee a team of **3–6 designers**, set the creative direction for projects from concept through completion, and serve as a key creative voice for Bolt — both internally and externally. The role requires strong leadership, exceptional taste, and the ability to clearly present and defend design ideas to clients.

As Creative Director, you’ll help define what Bolt *looks like* now — and where it’s headed next."/><meta property="og:image" content="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/4j6lg3tu/production/52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg"/><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><meta property="og:site_name" content="Bolt"/><meta property="og:locale" content="en_US"/><meta name="next-head-count" content="14"/><link data-next-font="" rel="preconnect" href="../index.html" crossorigin="anonymous"/><link rel="preload" href="../_next/static/css/03654ae58a6f64c1.css" as="style"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="../_next/static/css/03654ae58a6f64c1.css" data-n-g=""/><noscript data-n-css=""></noscript><script defer="" nomodule="" src="../_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js"></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/webpack-6ef43a8d4a395f49.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/framework-64ad27b21261a9ce.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/main-fc56ac81e639fb5e.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/pages/_app-e847f18df79b2407.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/276-306ef570f072595a.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/874-5abf096eed7b4aea.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/pages/jobs/[slug]-8e1d400c646908c9.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/T7iJTp4L-XJimUXsvzsi0/_buildManifest.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/T7iJTp4L-XJimUXsvzsi0/_ssgManifest.js" defer=""></script></head><body><div id="__next"><div><header class="px-unit pt-unit sticky top-0 text-white flex flex-col"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit border-current border-r"><div class="col-span-full grid grid-cols-2 "><div class="col-span-2 lg:col-span-1"><div class="col-span-full grid grid-cols-12"><div class="border-r border-b border-current col-span-6 pr-unit pb-2"><a class="text-current hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="../index