="../insights"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl leading-none hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Insights</p></a><a href="../contact"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl leading-none hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Contact</p></a></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit col-span-full pb-8 border-l border-current pl-unit pt-unit h-full"><div class="col-span-6 pr-6"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">Bolt Builds is a design, build, and fabrication firm located in Greenpoint, Brooklyn.</p><div class="pt-4"><a class="block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=202+Banker+Street+Brooklyn+NY+11222"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">202 Banker Street</p><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">Brooklyn, NY 11222</p></a><a class="text-current font-body text-xl block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="mailto:hello@bolt.build">hello@bolt.build</a><a class="text-current font-body text-xl block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="tel:+1 917-740-3463">+1 917-740-3463</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 border-t-0 lg:border-t border-x md:border-x-0 border-current"></div></div></div><div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10"><div class="cover-image-shim absolute inset-0 z-10"></div><img src="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcSet="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg&w=1920&q=75amp;qhttps://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg&w=3840&q=75;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x" alt="Bar Design NYC, Bolt, Bolt Builds, Bolt Builds NYC, Bolt Builds New York City, Bolt Design NYC, Bolt New York City, Boutique Design Agency New York, Custom Interior Design New York, Custom millwork NYC, Elegant Hospitality Interiors NYC, High-End Bar Design NYC, High-End Interior Design Agency NYC, High-End Retail Design New York, High-end Millwork NYC, Hospitality, Hospitality Interior Design New York, Innovative Hospitality Solutions New York, Luxery Millwork NYC, Luxury Bar Design NYC, Luxury Hospitality Consultants NYC, Luxury Millwork NYC, NYC Residential Interior Designers, New York, New York City, New York Design and Branding for Hospitality, New York Hospitality Branding, New York Retail Interior Design, Sophisticated Branding Agency NYC, luxury Hospitality Design NYC" width="1447" height="859" class="absolute object-cover w-full h-full z-0 inset-0" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 300vw, (max-width: 1000px) 200vw, 100vw"/></div><div class="border-x flex-1 flex flex-col justify-end"></div></header><div class="z-20 relative bg-white"><div class="sticky top-0 invisible"><div class="px-unit absolute left-0 right-0 bg-white"><div class="pt-unit border-black border-b"></div></div></div><div class="px-unit"><div class="pt-unit border-black border-x"><div class="sticky top-unit"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pt-2 pb-4"><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-3 pr-2"><p class="text-current font-body text-3xl">Creative Director </p></div><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-2"><h3 class="text-current font-body text-md">February 4, 2026</h3></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pt-8 pb-unit"><div class="col-start-1 col-end-13 md:col-start-2 md:col-end-12 lg:col-start-4 lg:col-end-12 xl:col-start-4 xl:col-end-10"><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>About Bolt</strong></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Bolt is a full-service <strong>Design + Build</strong> firm and fully insured <strong>General Contractor</strong> based in Brooklyn. We specialize in design-forward hospitality, retail, and residential projects that merge classical sensibility with innovative construction and fabrication methods. We believe that great design is only as strong as its execution — and that means being just as rigorous about budgets, schedules, and communication as we are about creative vision.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>The Role</strong></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Bolt is seeking a <strong>Creative Director</strong> to lead the design vision across hospitality, retail, and residential projects and to inspire, mentor, and guide a growing team of designers. This is a senior, studio-forward role for someone who is both creatively ambitious and deeply grounded in execution.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">You’ll oversee a team of <strong>3–6 designers</strong>, set the creative direction for projects from concept through completion, and serve as a key creative voice for Bolt — both internally and externally. The role requires strong leadership, exceptional taste, and the ability to clearly present and defend design ideas to clients.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">As Creative Director, you’ll help define what Bolt <em>looks like</em> now — and where it’s headed next.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Creative Vision &amp; Design Leadership</strong><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Define and uphold Bolt’s <strong>design vision</strong> across all hospitality, retail, and residential projects</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Set the creative tone for projects from <strong>initial concept through construction documentation and execution</strong></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Ensure design work is cohesive, intentional, and aligned with Bolt’s design standards and brand</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Lead design critiques and reviews, providing clear, constructive feedback that elevates the work</li></ul></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Team Leadership &amp; Mentorship</strong><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Manage, mentor, and inspire a team of 3–6 interior designers across varying levels of experience</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Set clear expectations for quality, deadlines, and design rigor</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Support professional growth through regular feedback, guidance, and skill development</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Foster a collaborative, curious, and accountable studio culture</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Help recruit, onboard, and develop future design talent as the team grows</li></ul></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Client Experience &amp; Presentation</strong><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Lead client-facing design presentations, articulating concepts, narratives, and decisions with confidence</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Translate client goals into strong, buildable design solutions</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Navigate client feedback with clarity and diplomacy, maintaining creative integrity while aligning with project realities</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Partner with leadership on pitches, proposals, and creative strategy for new business</li></ul></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Design Execution &amp; Cross-Disciplinary Collaboration</strong><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Work closely with Project Managers and construction teams to ensure design intent is carried through to the field</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Guide teams in resolving design challenges related to budget, schedule, and constructability</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Oversee FF&amp;E strategy, material palettes, lighting concepts, and key details</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Ensure drawing sets and design documentation meet Bolt’s quality standards</li></ul></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Creative Culture &amp; External Presence</strong><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Stay actively engaged with interior design trends, materials, and cultural influences</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Attend industry events, openings, and design conversations to keep Bolt creatively relevant</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Serve as a creative ambassador for Bolt within the design community</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Help evolve Bolt’s internal design processes, standards, and workflows over time</li></ul></li></ul><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Experience &amp; Skillset</strong><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">4 - 8 years of professional experience in interior design, with a strong portfolio of hospitality, retail, or high-end residential projects</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Proven experience leading or managing a design team</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Deep understanding of space planning, materials, lighting, FF&amp;E, detailing, and design storytelling</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Strong grasp of how design decisions translate into construction and execution</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Comfort working within a design-build model and collaborating closely with builders</li></ul></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Leadership &amp; Mindset</strong><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">A confident, thoughtful leader who can set direction while empowering others</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">High standards for design quality — and the ability to help others meet them</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Clear communicator who gives direct, constructive feedback with empathy</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Organized and reliable, able to manage multiple projects and priorities</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Comfortable making decisions and standing behind creative choices</li></ul></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Client &amp; Communication Strengths</strong><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Polished and compelling presentation skills</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Ability to communicate design intent clearly to clients, consultants, and internal teams</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Experience navigating client relationships and managing expectations</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Professional, calm, and confident under pressure</li></ul></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Creative Perspective &amp; Culture Fit</strong><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Strong point of view paired with curiosity and openness</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Deep interest in contemporary design, materials, and cultural context</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Excited to help shape a growing studio and its creative identity</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Energized by collaboration, iteration, and building things that last</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Based in NYC or willing to work fully in-person in Brooklyn</li></ul></li></ul><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>Why Bolt</strong></p><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>See your work built — and built fast.</strong> At Bolt, you won’t be stuck pushing paper for years before seeing results. Our projects move quickly, and the work you put in becomes something real, tangible, and lasting.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Be hands-on.</strong> You won’t be siloed behind a screen — you’ll be in the field, in meetings, on walk-throughs, and fully involved in the process from start to finish.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Work in the heart of Greenpoint.</strong> Our studio is based in one of Brooklyn’s most creative neighborhoods — surrounded by great food, inspiring spaces, and a thriving design community.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Join a company on the rise.</strong> Bolt is entering a new chapter of growth — and we’re building something special. You’ll help shape the future of the company, not just execute the present.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Build projects you’re proud of.</strong> From thoughtful restaurants to bold retail environments, you’ll be part of a team that sweats the details and cares deeply about design, craft, and execution.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Work with good people.</strong> We’re a tight-knit, driven team that takes pride in what we do — and has fun doing it. We value trust, accountability, and creative problem-solving.</li></ul><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>Compensation</strong></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">This is a <strong>full-time, in-person role</strong> based in our <strong>Greenpoint, Brooklyn</strong> studio.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">The base salary range for this position is <strong>$75,000–$105,000</strong>, depending on experience and qualifications. Bolt also offers performance-based bonus opportunities and the chance t